Package: metareport
Type: Package
Title: using opencpu server to render rmarkdown document on user uploaded data table
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Zhibin",
           family = "Ning",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ningzhibin@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Ning Zhibin <ningzhibin@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a way for general user to upload a data table, doing the analysis on an R server, and return the report from a browser or using API. In this package, an opencpu server was used to generate a quick report using rmarkdonw template. The package is an update of the old rmdocpu one. install ningzhibin/metalab from github first before usage.
